  <title>nmap-&nmap-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      Nmap is a utility for network exploration and security auditing. It
      supports ping scanning, port scanning and TCP/IP fingerprinting.
    </para>

